<div class="app-card-container">
	<div class="card">
		<h1>About Me</h1>

			<hr>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4">
				<%= image_tag "profile.jpeg", width: "300", alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img'  %>

				<div class="skills">
					<% @skills.each do |skill| %>
						<div class="skill">
							<h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
								<div class="progress">
									<div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
										role="progressbar"
										aria-valuenow="<%=skill.percent_utilized%>"
										aria-valuemax="100"
										style="width:<%=skill.percent_utilized %>%">
								
									</div>
								</div>	
						</div>
						
					<% end %>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-8">
				<p>“The difference between a successful person and others is not a lack of strength, not a lack of knowledge, but rather a lack of will.” 			– Vince Lombardi</p>

				<p>I have been doing development for about a year now.  I have enjoyed the learning process that I have gone through and want to keep that 			process going in the right direction.  I have been given tasks and have delivered them in a timely mannor and given daily updates to 				the client or representative so they know whats going on with the project.</p>
				<p>
					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#jobHistory"
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-controls="jobHistory"
					>
						Job History
					</button>	
					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#education"
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-controls="education"
					>
						Education
					</button>	
				</p>

				<p>
					<div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
						<div class="card card-block">
								JOBBBBBBBSSSSS 1
						</div>	
						<div class="card card-block">
								JOBBBBBBBSSSSS 2
						</div>	
					</div>
					<div class="collapse" id="education">
						<div class="card card-block">
								School 1
						</div>	
						<div class="card card-block">
								School 2
						</div>	
					</div>
				</p>

			</div>
		</div>		
	</div>
</div>



